# =============================================================================
# AI Provider Configuration
# =============================================================================
# Configure one or both providers. Each provider offers different capabilities.

# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# OPTION 1: Google AI Studio (Gemini)
# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Get your API key at: https://aistudio.google.com/app/apikey
#
# Capabilities:
#   - Text: Gemini 3.5 Flash / 3.1 Pro
#   - Image: Gemini 3 Image (Nano Banana)
#   - Video: Veo 3.1 (lite/fast/standard quality tiers)
#   - TTS: Gemini TTS (30 voices)
#   - Music: Lyria (background music, jingles)
#
# Single key:
GEMINI_API_KEY=your-api-key-here
#
# Multiple keys (for rate limit rotation):
# GEMINI_API_KEYS=key1,key2,key3

# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# OPTION 2: OpenRouter
# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Get your API key at: https://openrouter.ai/keys
#
# Capabilities:
#   - Text: 100+ models (GPT-4, Claude, Gemini, Llama, Mistral, etc.)
#   - Video: Seedance 2.0 (native lip-sync, integrated audio)
#   - STT: Whisper transcription
#
# Single key:
# OPENROUTER_API_KEY=sk-or-v1-your-key-here
#
# Multiple keys (for rate limit rotation):
# OPENROUTER_API_KEYS=key1,key2,key3
#
# Optional attribution headers sent with every OpenRouter request:
# OPENROUTER_REFERER=http://localhost   # HTTP-Referer header (default: http://localhost)
# OPENROUTER_TITLE=AI App               # X-Title header (default: "AI App")

# =============================================================================
# RunPod (optional) — get key: https://www.runpod.io/console/user/settings
# New account? Sign up via https://runpod.io?ref=z1r0sgie (referral link —
# load $10+ and get a one-time $5-500 bonus credit; most receive $5-10.
# Supports this project. Plain signup: https://runpod.io)
# =============================================================================
# Enables infiniteTalkLipsync: TRUE lip-sync of a character image to a
# PROVIDED audio file (user voice recordings/clones). Flat pricing per
# request: 480p $0.25 · 720p $0.50. No duration cap observed (13s+ ok).
#
# RUNPOD_API_KEY=rpa_your-key-here

# =============================================================================
# Provider Selection Guide
# =============================================================================
#
# BOTH CONFIGURED:
#   - Gemini: Best for video (Veo), music (Lyria), native Google quality
#   - OpenRouter: Best for Seedance (lip-sync), model variety, STT
#
# ONLY GEMINI:
#   - Full video, image, TTS, music support
#   - No Seedance lip-sync, no GPT-4/Claude access
#
# ONLY OPENROUTER:
#   - Seedance video, 100+ text models, STT
#   - No Lyria music generation

# =============================================================================
# Budget Enforcement
# =============================================================================
# The CLI hard-stops paid commands once a project hits its budget cap
# (BUDGET_EXCEEDED). To bypass the cap for ONE user-approved run, set
# BUDGET_OVERRIDE=1 per invocation — do NOT set it here permanently:
#   BUDGET_OVERRIDE=1 node workflows/cli.cjs <command> '<json-args>'
# See workflows/WORKFLOWS.md.
